Model fitting

model = fda(nlv = 2)
#model = fdasvd(nlv = 2)     # alternative algorithm (same result)
fit!(model, Xtrain, ytrain) 
fitm = model.fitm ;
@names fitm

(:T, :V, :Tcenters, :eig, :sstot, :W, :xmeans, :xscales, :weights, :lev, :n
i, :par)

lev = fitm.lev
